Samba-LDAP version 0.05

Samba::LDAP - Manage a Samba PDC with an LDAP Backend

CPAN Port of smbldap-tools found at http://samba.idealx.org/

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



DEPENDENCIES

None.


